    grammar to add new verbs or command structures.

When working with extensions, refer to their documentation to 
understand their specific structure and how to access and utilize 
their various components.

Creating Your Own Extensions: Sharing and Reusability

You can create your own extensions to share reusable code modules or 
implement unique features that you want to use across multiple 
projects. To create an extension, follow these steps:

