    Document your extension: Write clear and comprehensive 
    documentation that explains how to install, use, and integrate 
    your extension into Inform 6 projects.

Once you have created your extension, you can share it with the Inform 
6 community by uploading it to the IF Archive or other online 
repositories.

When creating extensions, consider the following:

